1
00:01:08,000 --> 00:01:08,519
Xiao Yifan

2
00:01:16,799 --> 00:01:18,159
Are you trying to ruin me?

3
00:01:18,799 --> 00:01:19,519
Su Yuanyuan

4
00:01:19,719 --> 00:01:21,560
How can you be as foolish as Fang Bing?

5
00:01:21,680 --> 00:01:23,159
Still can't tell right from wrong.

6
00:01:23,920 --> 00:01:25,239
We've known each other for years.

7
00:01:25,599 --> 00:01:27,280
I've loved you all these years.

8
00:01:27,959 --> 00:01:30,159
I don't blame you for bankrupting me.

9
00:01:30,359 --> 00:01:32,359
Or for having Fang Bing arrested.

10
00:01:32,879 --> 00:01:34,599
But you can't destroy me!

11
00:01:35,000 --> 00:01:36,000
Do you even have a conscience?

12
00:01:37,159 --> 00:01:38,079
Su Yuanyuan.

13
00:01:39,760 --> 00:01:40,719
My original intention

14
00:01:41,319 --> 00:01:42,159
was to help you.

15
00:01:43,799 --> 00:01:45,040
For us to cooperate and win together.

16
00:01:45,680 --> 00:01:46,560
But what about you?

17
00:01:47,079 --> 00:01:47,879
Just like Fang Bing.

18
00:01:48,599 --> 00:01:49,760
You were both too eager for quick gains.

19
00:01:51,079 --> 00:01:51,920
Fang Bing's bid rigging

20
00:01:52,239 --> 00:01:53,840
was an illegal act in itself.

21
00:01:55,680 --> 00:01:56,920
This current situation

22
00:01:57,519 --> 00:01:59,599
isn't what I wanted to see either.

23
00:02:01,480 --> 00:02:02,120
You should know,

24
00:02:03,439 --> 00:02:05,200
once you take the wrong path in life,

25
00:02:05,640 --> 00:02:06,920
turning back becomes very difficult.

26
00:02:18,879 --> 00:02:20,000
Oh, President Su.

27
00:02:20,199 --> 00:02:21,360
What kind of act is this?

28
00:02:23,840 --> 00:02:24,879
Why are you crying?

29
00:02:25,879 --> 00:02:27,199
Junjie, you're out of the hospital?

30
00:02:27,680 --> 00:02:28,199
If I didn't get out,

31
00:02:28,199 --> 00:02:28,800
I would've missed such

32
00:02:28,800 --> 00:02:29,879
a fascinating drama.

33
00:02:30,520 --> 00:02:31,479
Why does the way you two talk

34
00:02:31,479 --> 00:02:33,000
have a soap opera tone?

35
00:02:36,960 --> 00:02:37,599
Su Yuanyuan,

36
00:02:38,280 --> 00:02:40,319
you should go back and calm down.

37
00:02:42,599 --> 00:02:43,280
Xiao Yifan,

38
00:02:43,759 --> 00:02:45,000
are you going to help me or not?

39
00:02:50,719 --> 00:02:51,680
Su Yuanyuan,

40
00:02:52,080 --> 00:02:54,280
Though you tried to ruin my relationship

41
00:02:54,879 --> 00:02:56,800
and your husband ruined my family,

42
00:02:57,080 --> 00:02:59,120
we will never be like him,

43
00:02:59,360 --> 00:03:00,120
and drive people to a dead end.

44
00:03:07,240 --> 00:03:07,840
Su Yuanyuan,

45
00:03:09,280 --> 00:03:09,919
please leave.

46
00:03:23,240 --> 00:03:23,879
Chairman Zheng.

47
00:03:24,159 --> 00:03:25,319
You don't look so well.

48
00:03:25,680 --> 00:03:26,840
Are you feeling unwell?

49
00:03:28,759 --> 00:03:29,919
Look at what I received.

50
00:03:31,439 --> 00:03:32,280
An anonymous tip-off letter.

51
00:03:33,599 --> 00:03:34,919
Accusing you both of being involved

52
00:03:35,319 --> 00:03:36,400
in corruption during the project.

53
00:03:37,080 --> 00:03:37,919
See for yourselves.

54
00:03:45,639 --> 00:03:46,560
So cliché.

55
00:03:47,000 --> 00:03:47,560
A car accident.

56
00:03:47,560 --> 00:03:48,319
And kidnapping failed.

57
00:03:48,719 --> 00:03:49,840
Now they're pulling this bribery stunt.

58
00:03:50,000 --> 00:03:51,080
When did we ever take bribes?

59
00:03:51,319 --> 00:03:52,319
Do they call this evidence?

60
00:03:54,080 --> 00:03:54,560
Chairman Zheng.

61
00:03:55,000 --> 00:03:56,199
The accuser bears the burden of proof.

62
00:03:56,360 --> 00:03:57,319
Truth will prevail.

63
00:03:57,680 --> 00:03:58,280
The two of us

64
00:03:58,439 --> 00:03:59,759
would never tarnish your reputation.

65
00:04:00,360 --> 00:04:01,439
Of course I trust you both.

66
00:04:01,439 --> 00:04:02,159
Sit.

67
00:04:04,400 --> 00:04:05,800
The group needs to follow procedure.

68
00:04:06,039 --> 00:04:07,439
You'll need to cooperate with the probe.

69
00:04:07,919 --> 00:04:08,919
We promise to cooperate.

70
00:04:09,639 --> 00:04:10,599
And we'll hold up under scrutiny.

71
00:04:11,680 --> 00:04:12,759
I just came back to work.

72
00:04:12,840 --> 00:04:13,800
I won't get suspended, will I?

73
00:04:14,360 --> 00:04:15,199
It's not that serious.

74
00:04:15,280 --> 00:04:16,160
I'm telling you both

75
00:04:16,199 --> 00:04:17,759
just to give you a heads-up.

76
00:04:18,720 --> 00:04:20,800
Will the police believe Fang Bing's lies?

77
00:04:21,519 --> 00:04:23,199
Your head injury must still be acting up.

78
00:04:23,920 --> 00:04:24,839
Fang Bing's already been arrested.

79
00:04:25,639 --> 00:04:26,480
How could he

80
00:04:26,680 --> 00:04:27,480
frame us like this?

81
00:04:28,720 --> 00:04:30,000
You mean...

82
00:04:31,000 --> 00:04:31,959
What I mean is,

83
00:04:32,800 --> 00:04:33,800
Plot 7.

84
00:04:33,800 --> 00:04:35,839
Is Phase One's general contractor set?

85
00:04:36,399 --> 00:04:37,279
Don't worry, Chairman Zheng.

86
00:04:37,560 --> 00:04:38,399
Junjie and I

87
00:04:38,439 --> 00:04:39,319
will give it careful thought

88
00:04:39,480 --> 00:04:40,199
and get back to you.

89
00:04:46,040 --> 00:04:46,519
Bro.

90
00:04:47,000 --> 00:04:48,800
Playing riddles with Chairman Zheng?

91
00:04:48,959 --> 00:04:49,319
Spill it.

92
00:04:49,360 --> 00:04:49,920
Oh boy.

93
00:04:50,360 --> 00:04:51,879
My brother from another mother,

94
00:04:52,079 --> 00:04:53,600
your concussion is flaring up again.

95
00:04:54,519 --> 00:04:55,680
I was only hospitalized for a few days.

96
00:04:55,680 --> 00:04:56,720
And you're being all mysterious again.

97
00:04:57,319 --> 00:04:58,120
Come on, man.

98
00:04:58,279 --> 00:04:59,879
Use your brain for a second.

99
00:05:00,000 --> 00:05:00,720
Who else could it be?

100
00:05:01,800 --> 00:05:02,240
Who?

101
00:05:02,439 --> 00:05:03,319
Could it be Han Lin?

102
00:05:04,560 --> 00:05:05,759
Now you're sounding like yourself again.

103
00:05:08,199 --> 00:05:09,759
Su Yuanyuan's hysterical behavior,

104
00:05:09,959 --> 00:05:11,959
didn't it move you at all?

105
00:05:15,639 --> 00:05:16,759
She really has had it rough.

106
00:05:18,720 --> 00:05:19,920
Su Yuanyuan went to Yang Hui,

107
00:05:19,920 --> 00:05:21,040
and to my wife,

108
00:05:21,120 --> 00:05:21,959
and even knelt at your door begging.

109
00:05:22,399 --> 00:05:23,199
Going bankrupt,

110
00:05:23,199 --> 00:05:23,959
her husband in prison,

111
00:05:24,199 --> 00:05:25,120
she really has it rough.

112
00:05:25,639 --> 00:05:26,920
President He Junjie,

113
00:05:27,680 --> 00:05:29,000
time to get back to business.

114
00:05:32,839 --> 00:05:34,040
For Plot 7 Phase One's general contractor,

115
00:05:34,040 --> 00:05:35,000
which company did you pick?

116
00:05:36,120 --> 00:05:37,360
I think this company looks good.

117
00:05:38,720 --> 00:05:39,959
Alright, your call.

118
00:05:44,959 --> 00:05:45,319
President Fang.

119
00:05:45,720 --> 00:05:47,399
About Plot 7 Phase One's general contract,

120
00:05:47,759 --> 00:05:49,000
I was notified to prepare for signing.

121
00:05:50,079 --> 00:05:50,399
Good.

122
00:05:51,160 --> 00:05:52,079
Stick to the plan.

123
00:05:52,920 --> 00:05:54,000
When the time is right,

124
00:05:54,399 --> 00:05:55,560
file a massive damages lawsuit.

125
00:05:56,120 --> 00:05:56,639
Understood.

126
00:05:57,240 --> 00:05:58,240
Wait for my good news.

127
00:05:59,560 --> 00:06:00,800
But don't rush it.

128
00:06:01,319 --> 00:06:01,920
One step at a time.

129
00:06:03,160 --> 00:06:03,639
Mm.

130
00:06:20,360 --> 00:06:21,160
Is there money on my face?

131
00:06:21,240 --> 00:06:21,920
Why keep staring at me?

132
00:06:23,839 --> 00:06:25,399
It's the plan for Plot 7.

133
00:06:31,759 --> 00:06:32,360
What do you mean?

134
00:06:34,040 --> 00:06:35,680
Once Plot 7 Phase One's general contractor

135
00:06:35,680 --> 00:06:36,839
is confirmed,

136
00:06:37,319 --> 00:06:39,279
what about Phase Two's tourism project?

137
00:06:42,040 --> 00:06:42,879
On the same wavelength.

138
00:06:44,399 --> 00:06:45,519
The later phases of Plot 7

139
00:06:45,720 --> 00:06:47,160
still have hundreds of thousands of sqm.

140
00:06:47,439 --> 00:06:48,720
There's huge development potential.

141
00:06:49,839 --> 00:06:51,279
Let's put together a comprehensive plan.

142
00:06:52,000 --> 00:06:52,639
When it's ready,

143
00:06:53,279 --> 00:06:53,879
we'll submit it to Chairman Zheng.

144
00:06:55,720 --> 00:06:56,399
Got it.

145
00:06:56,920 --> 00:06:57,480
Let's get to work.

146
00:07:01,319 --> 00:07:01,800
This one,

147
00:07:02,120 --> 00:07:02,600
we can do this.

148
00:07:03,439 --> 00:07:04,160
This area here,

149
00:07:04,319 --> 00:07:05,040
that works, right?

150
00:07:05,800 --> 00:07:06,519
Move it over here.

151
00:07:07,600 --> 00:07:09,279
We can sell this area at a higher price.

152
00:07:09,879 --> 00:07:12,000
Like a gym or something.

153
00:07:17,160 --> 00:07:17,759
Right now,

154
00:07:17,759 --> 00:07:18,720
it's past mealtime.

155
00:07:18,720 --> 00:07:20,399
Just have some water for now.

156
00:07:20,759 --> 00:07:22,600
Next time, I'll treat you to a big meal.

157
00:07:23,079 --> 00:07:23,720
Oh, come on.

158
00:07:24,040 --> 00:07:25,279
No need to be so polite with me.

159
00:07:26,040 --> 00:07:27,240
The reason I asked you here

160
00:07:27,600 --> 00:07:28,279
is because there's something

161
00:07:28,560 --> 00:07:29,439
I want your opinion on.

162
00:07:29,920 --> 00:07:30,399
What is it?

163
00:07:30,879 --> 00:07:31,519
Pregnant with a second child?

164
00:07:33,959 --> 00:07:35,600
Why would I ask you about that?

165
00:07:35,600 --> 00:07:36,879
I'd obviously ask my husband.

166
00:07:36,879 --> 00:07:37,879
Honestly.

167
00:07:40,399 --> 00:07:41,000
Well, go on then.

168
00:07:41,240 --> 00:07:41,720
What is it?

169
00:07:42,879 --> 00:07:43,879
I think

170
00:07:44,199 --> 00:07:46,399
Su Yuanyuan isn't really a wicked person.

171
00:07:46,399 --> 00:07:47,600
Her state lately

172
00:07:47,600 --> 00:07:48,480
seems a bit off.

173
00:07:49,000 --> 00:07:49,800
What do you mean?

174
00:07:50,560 --> 00:07:52,360
Her husband did all kinds of evil.

175
00:07:52,480 --> 00:07:54,120
He deserved the legal punishment.

176
00:07:55,319 --> 00:07:56,920
Don't tell me you feel sorry for her.

177
00:07:57,800 --> 00:07:58,560
No, that's not it.

178
00:07:59,319 --> 00:08:02,439
Given Su Yuanyuan's strong personality,

179
00:08:02,800 --> 00:08:03,920
when she faces trouble,

180
00:08:03,920 --> 00:08:04,639
her first instinct

181
00:08:04,639 --> 00:08:05,720
should be to find a way to save herself,

182
00:08:06,319 --> 00:08:07,759
not act like a broken record,

183
00:08:08,319 --> 00:08:09,040
crying to everyone,

184
00:08:09,040 --> 00:08:09,680
and begging.

185
00:08:11,319 --> 00:08:12,600
You've got a point.

186
00:08:12,600 --> 00:08:13,920
With her personality,

187
00:08:13,920 --> 00:08:14,639
being so headstrong,

188
00:08:15,519 --> 00:08:17,040
her current behavior

189
00:08:17,040 --> 00:08:17,920
really doesn't add up.

190
00:08:19,319 --> 00:08:20,680
So what does this

191
00:08:21,199 --> 00:08:22,040
indicate then?

192
00:08:22,920 --> 00:08:23,680
A mental illness.

193
00:08:24,319 --> 00:08:25,480
No close friends,

194
00:08:26,360 --> 00:08:26,920
bankruptcy,

195
00:08:27,079 --> 00:08:27,839
husband arrested,

196
00:08:28,040 --> 00:08:29,680
and then everyone isolating her,

197
00:08:29,680 --> 00:08:30,560
leading to a split personality.

198
00:08:31,079 --> 00:08:32,840
You sound like a psychiatrist.

199
00:08:34,159 --> 00:08:34,840
Why don't we take this chance,

200
00:08:35,000 --> 00:08:35,679
while we still have time,

201
00:08:35,879 --> 00:08:36,440
and go find her?

202
00:08:37,320 --> 00:08:37,840
I'm not going.

203
00:08:37,840 --> 00:08:39,360
I'm not as generous as you.

204
00:08:40,480 --> 00:08:41,039
Come on.

205
00:08:41,120 --> 00:08:41,679
I'll drive.

206
00:08:42,200 --> 00:08:42,600
Get up.

207
00:08:43,720 --> 00:08:45,279
Fine, for your sake.

208
00:08:58,159 --> 00:08:59,240
President Su.

209
00:09:01,360 --> 00:09:02,279
Good afternoon.

210
00:09:03,279 --> 00:09:04,200
What are you doing here?

211
00:09:04,519 --> 00:09:05,399
Here to settle scores?

212
00:09:12,240 --> 00:09:13,960
The law will deal with your husband.

213
00:09:14,200 --> 00:09:15,399
Between us personally,

214
00:09:15,480 --> 00:09:16,879
there's no real grudge to speak of.

215
00:09:18,639 --> 00:09:20,000
Then why are you two here?

216
00:09:20,919 --> 00:09:21,879
Let me make this clear.

217
00:09:22,120 --> 00:09:24,399
I only came for Yang Hui's sake.

218
00:09:25,080 --> 00:09:26,720
But I don't intend to forgive

219
00:09:26,720 --> 00:09:28,159
the things your husband did.

220
00:09:28,960 --> 00:09:29,799
President Su.

221
00:09:30,440 --> 00:09:31,240
As a woman,

222
00:09:31,440 --> 00:09:32,559
I do sympathize with you.

223
00:09:33,320 --> 00:09:34,879
You've been through a string of blows,

224
00:09:35,240 --> 00:09:37,600
and with no one there to help you,

225
00:09:38,120 --> 00:09:38,679
you ended up doing things

226
00:09:38,679 --> 00:09:40,159
that were out of the ordinary.

227
00:09:40,600 --> 00:09:42,480
Honestly, you have your own strengths.

228
00:09:43,120 --> 00:09:44,559
You used to dominate the business world.

229
00:09:46,000 --> 00:09:48,440
You shouldn't be so defeated now.

230
00:09:50,720 --> 00:09:52,879
I really didn't want to hurt anyone.

231
00:09:53,399 --> 00:09:55,120
I just couldn't accept it.

232
00:09:56,159 --> 00:09:57,159
And as time went on,

233
00:09:57,159 --> 00:09:58,639
I had no idea what to do anymore.

234
00:10:00,320 --> 00:10:02,240
The banks demand payment every day.

235
00:10:02,279 --> 00:10:03,440
Every single day.

236
00:10:04,120 --> 00:10:05,840
Fang Bing is my husband.

237
00:10:06,559 --> 00:10:08,000
What was I supposed to do?

238
00:10:09,279 --> 00:10:10,159
Right now I'm really

239
00:10:10,159 --> 00:10:11,440
about to fall apart.

240
00:10:17,039 --> 00:10:19,559
My life is in complete chaos now.

241
00:10:22,720 --> 00:10:23,960
Honestly,

242
00:10:24,039 --> 00:10:25,279
you've had it rough too.

243
00:10:25,840 --> 00:10:28,200
Sometimes for a woman in business,

244
00:10:28,399 --> 00:10:30,360
it really is much harder than for men.

245
00:10:30,639 --> 00:10:31,799
But you shouldn't have

246
00:10:31,799 --> 00:10:32,840
used such extreme methods

247
00:10:32,840 --> 00:10:34,279
to gain advantage for yourselves.
